    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，英国改革党领衔，小党派得势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-minor-parties-push-up-led-by-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奈杰尔·法拉奇领导的改革英国在民意调查中支持率持续上升，周四在彭博英国民意调查中连续第四天创下历史新高，而首相里希·苏纳克领导的执政党保守党支持率则跌至新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-minor-parties-push-up-led-by-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 10:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行顾问称中国出口应重点关注南半球国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/china-should-focus-exports-on-global-south-says-pboc-adviser</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行一位顾问表示，中国政府应支持出口向发展中国家转移，这样才能找到有能力消化其工业产出的市场，并缓解与其他贸易伙伴的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/china-should-focus-exports-on-global-south-says-pboc-adviser</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 09:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟同意对俄罗斯实施首批制裁，打击部分液化天然气运输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/eu-agrees-russia-sanctions-hitting-lng-shipments-chinese-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟批准了针对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的新一轮制裁措施，寻求通过将制裁范围扩大到俄罗斯的帮凶网络来加强限制措施的执行，并打击莫斯科的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/eu-agrees-russia-sanctions-hitting-lng-shipments-chinese-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 08:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西藏流亡领袖呼吁世界敦促中国进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/exiled-tibet-leader-calls-on-world-to-pressure-china-into-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西藏流亡政府首脑鼓励各国加入美国行列，向中国施压，要求其恢复与西藏官员的直接谈判，并称最近通过的加强美国对该地区海外领导人支持的立法是一个重要的新工具。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/exiled-tibet-leader-calls-on-world-to-pressure-china-into-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果勒庞领导的政党赢得大选，法国绿色能源转型将面临停滞的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/france-s-green-energy-shift-at-risk-of-stalling-if-le-pen-s-party-wins-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国扩大可再生能源、摆脱化石燃料的计划正面临玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼民族主义政党的威胁，该政党可能会在数周内的立法选举中赢得最多席位，并废除关键的环境政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/france-s-green-energy-shift-at-risk-of-stalling-if-le-pen-s-party-wins-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
